Criminal Code – Prison Sentence: The effect of the Kazenelson criminal law decision on legal advice to workers. In concluding a case commentary in the previous issue of this newsletter, I asked: &ldquo;Has Kazenelson changed the rules of engagement for going to work? Should workers worry about this?&rdquo;
In this polemic, I try to explain why my answers are: yes &amp; yes.
The Kazenelson case is the first major conviction under the Westray-changed Criminal Code.
